{"type": "article", "id": 19066, "title": "太阳能充电器", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-15T09:27:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 67, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134740Ak0MuIyn9zwct6lK.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是丹麦的设计公司 infinityPV 研发出来的太阳能充电器，从充电器中间可以展开一张超薄的太阳能面板，然后放在阳光下蓄电。蓄电之后直接收回在 11.3 厘米长的容器中，方便携带。这款充电器可以储存 2600mAh 的电量，可与手机、移动电源等设备相连。产品目前正在众筹，<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/infinitypv/heli-on?ref=nav_search\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145739LK5PIoFxgCOWjsXH.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261457401ZypEjnu24JfmMOk.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145740IDsMtCvoSfQEl1uL.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"614\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145741rTenaiCXd4UfNx71.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"580\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70904645\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}